小說<br />\n包你到n1</blockquote><br />\n咁listening呢？"},{"pid":"d70790754960889ffce025622d8a9b4ecd3f92df","tid":387851,"uid":27728,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:15:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇小說<br />\n包你到n1</blockquote><br />\nN4 睇小說會唔會太難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282d21f8f56e5e2223507099becee44159652bdb","tid":387851,"uid":48680,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:44:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇小說<br />\n包你到n1</blockquote><br />\nN4 睇小說會唔會太難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我n5開始已經睇 <br />\n漢仔鳩估 唔明文法上網查<br />\n諗自已 n幾意義不大<br />\n<br />\nhandle 到小說n2 讀解訓住過<br />\n利申:n2 讀解60/60<br />\n但文法弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5560a1023aad5465ee55f37b9240eb07fb66b81","tid":387851,"uid":55296,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:58:00.000Z","msg":"讀到上n1 依然會覺得自己無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55acf7c6808f68fbb23b15215cff16290c0d984","tid":387851,"uid":30022,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:02:47.000Z","msg":"考完n1先係學日文嘅開始"},{"pid":"a43f2fa3258968632e9ac7fff9567ab1c7b4da04","tid":387851,"uid":125208,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:07:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀到上n1 依然會覺得自己無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同感, 3,4年前考完都冇咩機會用, 感覺而家重衰過N4程度"},{"pid":"f5f3fbc6fc4d29a1d7b8ebb535d832a325ecf05a","tid":387851,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T14:29:17.000Z","msg":"非常重要　推一推文先<br />\n<br />\n再問, 有咩天書介紹"},{"pid":"57c0058ee215d5638ca6c047bd263aa13c6d1252","tid":387851,"uid":64953,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T14:31:16.000Z","msg":"撘單問自學N3 用咩書好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6971a53e6e7bb3f4cdaeabc7f92f7b3757d3f26","tid":387851,"uid":35273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:00:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撘單問自學N3 用咩書好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8403bcd695605dfa0f957e41d85a899734255eb","tid":387851,"uid":13586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:02:04.000Z","msg":"打算12月考n4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664b1e0cd31925cc95f7b2270b4847d0098ad031","tid":387851,"uid":48084,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:02:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>撘單問自學N3 用咩書好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淘寶紅藍書，n4能力左右，1個星期食哂兩本pass左，不過考完就唔記得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e77fdedef9eea1ea109bba24db7d29d93563d5","tid":387851,"uid":41308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:16:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>撘單問自學N3 用咩書好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淘寶紅藍書，n4能力左右，1個星期食哂兩本pass左，不過考完就唔記得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁N2係唔係都係呢本, 同埋正式名係咩"},{"pid":"f985827140a86555b29d265a6f32eac43a9e0c2b","tid":387851,"uid":34789,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:02:27.000Z","msg":"要張CERT嚟搵工？<br />\n比你考到但係咪應用到先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47408200a147d61472a5b8aef2042b30c5aa49b","tid":387851,"uid":38143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:24:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撘單問自學N3 用咩書好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nN4同n3分別唔大"},{"pid":"438cf1b6e9dbd5280fe1de91a357f221143a7c44","tid":387851,"uid":38143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:30:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要張CERT嚟搵工？<br />\n比你考到但係咪應用到先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係講呢樣野<br />\n你話你日文本身好好就話補返張cert啫<br />\nN4程度比你碌張n2返黎咪又係要時間追<br />\n<br />\n你話點都要碌張cert既話我會去田園買兩本華東理工雞精書算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b48de821c6291d667ed753c58729902edfc5c79","tid":387851,"uid":65756,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:36:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要張CERT嚟搵工？<br />\n比你考到但係咪應用到先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係講呢樣野<br />\n你話你日文本身好好就話補返張cert啫<br />\nN4程度比你碌張n2返黎咪又係要時間追<br />\n<br />\n你話點都要碌張cert既話我會去<span style=\"color: red;\">田園</span>買兩本華東理工雞精書算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇左做園田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9899d2b54c5f1c27c5e9a6bd1b8d408cb3be40","tid":387851,"uid":41308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要張CERT嚟搵工？<br />\n比你考到但係咪應用到先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係講呢樣野<br />\n你話你日文本身好好就話補返張cert啫<br />\nN4程度比你碌張n2返黎咪又係要時間追<br />\n<br />\n你話點都要碌張cert既話我會去田園買兩本華東理工雞精書算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n碌左先算啦。你係要入到個日文環境 日文先會有進步"},{"pid":"59dd98e67972de44e41d7df5b420463971088562","tid":387851,"uid":46020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:32:57.000Z","msg":"同問N4兩個月內用咩書變N3?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀完大家的日本語1-50之後唔知買咩書係啱用比我跟住讀上去"},{"pid":"b792c9913f7b955fad17d20f0fc4a1216ab4715f","tid":387851,"uid":114088,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:40:46.000Z","msg":"其實係你地勁定出面D日文班進度慢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n學成年先N5, N4又要用多年<br />\n<br />\n但我聽人講N3夠晒喺日本職場以外生活用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d95864a9d03233ad2fd17e4e254fd96702e1a0a","tid":387851,"uid":125208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:47:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係你地勁定出面D日文班進度慢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n學成年先N5, N4又要用多年<br />\n<br />\n但我聽人講N3夠晒喺日本職場以外生活用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出面多數每個禮拜先1,2堂當然慢<br />\n有d有intensive班3,4個月就可以學晒必要grammar, 當然都會好少時間消化同自己練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083f3af18f3804e63bfabb547c92fac277f340bc","tid":387851,"uid":15323,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:01:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係你地勁定出面D日文班進度慢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n學成年先N5, N4又要用多年<br />\n<br />\n但我聽人講N3夠晒喺日本職場以外生活用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有一堆真係勁，本身語文能力好<br />\n又生活係充滿日文環境<br />\n<br />\n有一堆考完n2但乜都唔記得<br />\n問返佢n4 d野都仲有甩溜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學語文建議打好基礎，你再學上去先會容易"},{"pid":"76405ba258645db58471bc1c63e618d431df24b6","tid":387851,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:23:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係你地勁定出面D日文班進度慢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n學成年先N5, N4又要用多年<br />\n<br />\n但我聽人講N3夠晒喺日本職場以外生活用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但職場唔夠用埋 職場黎講 N1低分合格都唔係好夠<br />\n出面真係好慢 但唔上堂 又無機會練習"},{"pid":"963c897d405bd1160a897294753ef35c1463b82b","tid":387851,"uid":144416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:28:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇小說<br />\n包你到n1</blockquote><br />\nN4 睇小說會唔會太難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我n5開始已經睇 <br />\n漢仔鳩估 唔明文法上網查<br />\n諗自已 n幾意義不大<br />\n<br />\nhandle 到小說n2 讀解訓住過<br />\n利申:n2 讀解60/60<br />\n但文法弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n勁喎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下有冇小說推介？<br />\n<br />\n利申：N4"},{"pid":"eb227555e04596540f0bd7abc3131acd72493e08","tid":387851,"uid":74717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:32:02.000Z","msg":"下年讀完N1班想再進修, 有無巴打有類似經驗分享下?"},{"pid":"f90197be471312cebfd350de1e45f62db3f8480b","tid":387851,"uid":128127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:40:18.000Z","msg":"我都係今年12月考N2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4bd83c0efd911fd6f283a182d6b970332eaf3b6","tid":387851,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:46:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係今年12月考N2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大家一齊研究下 <br />\n一緒に勉強しましょう<br />\n頑張れ"},{"pid":"0b958c40e09cbc020f19d61cabfb3b6240ea4f07","tid":387851,"uid":85965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:48:17.000Z","msg":"你n4係高定低分過？你而家文法，listening 真正水準又去到邊個程度先？"},{"pid":"afd744c67bf78120fff5bbf1c1c84b46d2f1e034","tid":387851,"uid":47365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:58:31.000Z","msg":"報左12月n3<img src=\"/asset