<br />\n因為n4其實好易，俾d挑戰自己先有進步"},{"pid":"b4cb2dd26c3f742ee67aa9060a8528f6953acdc3","tid":387851,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T08:16:14.000Z","msg":"N6，0知識<br />\n可以點入手？"},{"pid":"3842faf38ea69cc63cddb1c0e9fd1556d9d20703","tid":387851,"uid":85965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T08:21:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩自學覺得好迷茫<br />\n屋企有set進學日本語同埋支發音筆<br />\n但係本野全部日文有時唔明佢教乜<br />\n我想搵d用中文教文法既書 感覺會易理解d<br />\n請問有邊本書最岩初學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我暫時個目標係年尾去日本可以基本溝通到<br />\n大家覺得有冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想打好基礎都係搵人教好d<br />\n自學既話我睇過fb台仔 音速日語notes<br />\n佢由初至中既文法都有<br />\n個人覺得佢寫得唔錯，幾易明<br />\n<br />\n如果你基本溝通意思係應用，對答到罐頭對話<br />\n咁就唔難既"},{"pid":"72ddf3ded3c434f953d0b2a5a98e835c723c94b9","tid":387851,"uid":85965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T08:22:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>N6，0知識<br />\n可以點入手？</blockquote><br />\n培養對日文既興趣再學左50音先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db6ab9974a40572923cf451b9850519e16b3f72","tid":387851,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:26:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>N6，0知識<br />\n可以點入手？</blockquote><br />\n培養對日文既興趣再學左50音先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n50音係邊學"},{"pid":"722b136a5d98cb25633fed4d6e972a5bffe02fb8","tid":387851,"uid":104312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:40:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>N6，0知識<br />\n可以點入手？</blockquote><br />\n培養對日文既興趣再學左50音先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n50音係邊學</blockquote><br />\n上網搵都有 求其打50音就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f24c28e79b82293127172db9c4567d912764afa","tid":387851,"uid":104312,"like":1,"